dataLineage.statement:
Layer was downloaded by ITOS in an email from the IMO. It was then analyzed by ITOS for errors. Those errors were corrected and then the layer was sent back to UNOCHA as a feature class within a file geodatabase.
The following errors were found and fixed by ITOS: 1. Two small gap errors were fixed. One is located between admin 2 units "Boke" and "Boffa" and the other is between admin 3 units "Balizia" and "Daro". 2. Multipart sliver error fixed for admin 3 unit "Diaraguerela".
